We will get through this together. Power in numbers. #GodWins

data.text:
@joncoopertweets @MeidasTouch 34 US Senate seats get filled in 2022. In election-speak, that's like a week or two away.

It never ends. Local elections, primaries, general elections, run-offs - it's a never-ending cycle spinning from one election to another.

We need to be able to SAFELY vote online.
